data.description: Beautifully maintained one story home shows pride in ownership. Perfect for a young family or someone looking to downsize. The house is move in ready or you can put your own personal touches to make it home. The location is convenient to 75 or 190. This charming home has 3 good sized bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 car garage. The backyard is perfect for entertaining so peaceful. Walking distance to parks and schools. Don't miss this great home.
